\caption[]{\textbf{System Overview} Our system consists of three main parts: a gateway, a processing group, and a data warehousing group. The gateway accepts receipt requests and passed them on to the processing group. Once a receipt has been processed it is passed to the data warehousing group to be stored for future use.}
\label{fig:overview}
\end{figure*}